<b>When you need to grip with power and endurance</b>

00:00:03.072 --> 00:00:04.608
<b>relax your index finger</b>

00:00:04.864 --> 00:00:07.424
<b>and grip with your middle, ring and little finger.</b>

00:00:07.936 --> 00:00:12.288
<b>Relaxing your index finger reduces the strain </b>
<b>on smaller muscles and tendons.</b>

00:00:13.056 --> 00:00:15.516
<b>This part of your hand is built for precision work.</b>

00:00:16.128 --> 00:00:17.408
<b>Hanging weight on this finger,</b>

00:00:17.920 --> 00:00:22.784
<b>or repetitively squeezing with this finger, </b>
<b>can over-stress these precision muscles and tendons.</b>

00:00:23.552 --> 00:00:25.088
<b>Relax your index finger,</b>

00:00:25.600 --> 00:00:27.648
<b>to reduce stress and boost performance.</b>

